  "stem": "<p>The function <em>f</em> is defined by <math><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn></math>. What is the positive value of <em>x</em> for which <math><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>24</mn></math>?</p>",
